If something happened at the Trainer base and I missed it, please tell me.

::Neody/Slayer/Crater/Killfest::

Neody's eyes widen slightly as he sees Crater at the battle, making a mental note to talk to him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Crater stays ready for battle again, glancing at Darkfate to see if he would do anything.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Slayer growls, feeling rather helpless where he was. There was an army of Predacons around him, attacking the base of the faction that he belonged to, and he could do nothing to help but wait and hope.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killfest remains still, as he has no other choice.
